      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VALENZUELA (4) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at this track but was a Grade 5 winner two back at Cannington. This looks easier and expected to bounce back. LOCHINVAR HUMMER (1) was never in contention last time after drifting back at this track, but prior to that won easily by 5.5 lengths at this track (34.17) beating Weblec Memphis in a Grade 5 H on February 28. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Better than last start and can bounce back. SHIMA BLUSH (6) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 34.25 beating Ross The Boss. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Expected to feature again. WARM COCKLES (8) must be included on latest effort.",
